hooks are javascript func. 
with the help of hooks we can implement state and lifecycle methods in functional component
hooks were starts with 'use' 
hooks were added in react library in verion 16.8
to use hooks we have to name import from react library.

rules :
we can use hooks inside fucntional component only.
we cant use hooks inside class based components or in plane js
we cant use hook inside a loop ,conndition or inside nested condition.
we have to call a hook at top level01
we have ot  usehook at same level to return statement. 
if we are creating our custom hook we have to start its name with 'use' word.


